{"article_id":"7qJtHeiuJwIULMSc","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Congressional Republicans may find inspiration from the King of Rock and Roll","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"when comes to passing their replacement bill for ObamaCare .","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"Imagine Elvis Presley","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"crooning his 1960 number one single , \" It ' s Now or Never . \"","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"\" We have a choice , \"","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"proffered House Ways and Means Committee Chairman Kevin Brady , R-Texas , one of the authors of the health care blueprint .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"\" We can act now","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"or we can keep fiddling around","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"and squander this opportunity","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"to repeal ObamaCare . \"","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"In 2009 and 2010 , Republicans railed against Democrats","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"as they relied almost exclusively on their own members","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"to approve ObamaCare .","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"Now Republicans are going it alone","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"to repeal ObamaCare","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"and adopt their own health care package .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"But some conservative lawmakers and interest groups alike are upbraiding the GOP legislation .","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"It only takes a few renegades in both the House and Senate to incinerate the plan .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"\" It ' s ObamaCare-lite , \"","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"argued Sen. Rand Paul , R-Ky.","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"\" We have to admit","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"we are divided on replacement . \"","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"\" Obviously we have serious concerns , \"","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"said House Freedom Caucus co-chairman Rep. Mark Meadows , R-N.","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"C .","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"Michael Needham , the head of the conservative policy organization Heritage Action , declared","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"there was \" no significant difference \" between the GOP replacement package and ObamaCare .","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"Passage of the Republican health care bill comes down to the numbers .","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"The GOP can only lose 21 votes","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"before the measure fails on a party-line vote .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"The Freedom Caucus has a bylaw","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"that compels its members to vote as a bloc","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"if 80 percent of its 40-plus members feel the same on a given issue .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"That ' s more than enough","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"to incinerate the health care measure on the floor .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"That ' s why the Trump administration deployed Budget Director and Freedom Caucus founder Mick Mulvaney","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"to liaise with congressional Republicans .","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"Vice President Pence also paid a visit to the Freedom Caucus .","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"Meadows says","depth":15},{"id":39,"text":"Pence told his members","depth":16},{"id":40,"text":"the bill was still open for negotiation .","depth":16},{"id":41,"text":"But after a lunch meeting with Senate Republicans , Pence suggested","depth":15},{"id":42,"text":"the bill might not be that agile .","depth":15},{"id":43,"text":"\" This is the bill , \"","depth":15},{"id":44,"text":"said Pence .","depth":15},{"id":45,"text":"\" The president supports it","depth":15},{"id":46,"text":"and looks forward to working directly on this bill . \"","depth":15},{"id":47,"text":"Rep. Mark Sanford , R-S.C. , suggested","depth":14},{"id":48,"text":"Trump was in negotiation mode .","depth":14},{"id":49,"text":"\" What we have here is an opening bid , \"","depth":15},{"id":50,"text":"said Sanford .","depth":15},{"id":51,"text":"\" There better not be a rule","depth":16},{"id":52,"text":"that bans amendments","depth":17},{"id":53,"text":"which are badly needed","depth":18},{"id":54,"text":"to fix this bill , \"","depth":18},{"id":55,"text":"said Rep. Louie Gohmert , R-Texas .","depth":15},{"id":56,"text":"The Freedom Caucus is a little like the Democratic Blue Dog coalition","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"which was key","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"to approving ObamaCare .","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"The Blue Dogs , a group of conservative Democrats , are still around .","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"There just aren ' t many left in the House Democratic Caucus these days .","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"The Blue Dogs ,","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"when their numbers were bigger ,","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"often made a lot of noise .","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"But","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"when then-House Speaker Nancy Pelosi , D-Calif. , needed Blue Dog votes ,","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"most of them heeled .","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"In March , 2010 , Pelosi lacked the votes","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"to pass the final version of the Affordable Care Act","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"( ACA ) .","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"So she authorized the House Rules Committee to allow but two amendments before the decisive ObamaCare debate .","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"One amendment was for a Republican health care plan .","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"The other amendment was a proposal","depth":15},{"id":73,"text":"written by then-Rep. Bart Stupak , D-Mich .","depth":15},{"id":74,"text":"The \" Stupak Amendment \" constructed an additional firewall","depth":15},{"id":75,"text":"to ensure","depth":16},{"id":76,"text":"that federal dollars wouldn ' t cover abortions .","depth":16},{"id":77,"text":"The Stupak amendment ultimately courted the support of just enough conservative , pro-life Democrats .","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"The House okayed the first iteration of Obamacare 220-215 .","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"The question now is how might lawmakers contour the GOP health care plan to their liking .","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"Also ,","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"as Gohmert asks ,","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"what amendments might the GOP brass permit ?","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"Is there flexibility ?","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"What happens","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"if just enough Republicans balk at the bill ?","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"Does the president light them up on Twitter ?","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"\" The American Health Care Act","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"( ACHA )","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"is the first test of presidential legislative power , \"","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"suggested House Republican Chief Deputy Whip Patrick McHenry , R-N.C. , after a White House confab .","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"Meadows understands the risks","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"some conservatives could face","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"should they buck Trump .","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"\" The president has a powerful bully pulpit and a powerful tweet , \"","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"said Meadows .","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"\" I would not want to take him on in either of those concerns . \"","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"House Speaker Paul Ryan , R-Wis. , may not emulate Pelosi","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"when it comes to whipping a vote .","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"But he sure exuded confidence Tuesday .","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"\" We will have 218 votes , \"","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"predicted Ryan .","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"\" I can guarantee you . \"","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"Of course , Ryan only needs 216","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"to approve the ACHA .","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"Ryan and other ACHA supporters must court members of the Freedom Caucus for their votes .","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"Some top GOP aides and even lawmakers spent the past few days trolling conservatives","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"who weren ' t on board ,","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"privately bad-mouthing them .","depth":6},{"id":109,"text":"House Energy and Commerce Committee Chairman Greg Walden , R-Ore. , co-wrote the ObamaCare replacement bill alongside Kevin Brady .","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"Rand Paul embarked on a Quixotic ,","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"if faux ,","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"quest","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"to find the \" secret location \" of the bill last week .","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"When the House Republican leadership released the bill ,","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"Walden ' s crew \" hand-delivered \" a copy of the legislation to Paul ' s office","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"and tweeted a photo of the consignment .","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"The margin","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"to pass this bill","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"could be tight .","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"Consider the narrow vote","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"engineered by Pelosi","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"to pass ObamaCare .","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"Ryan and other Republican leaders must earn the support of skeptics in their own party ,","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"not antagonize them .","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"Ryan wants to pass the bill by the end of the month .","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell , R-Ky. , hopes to follow suit in early April .","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"The bill probably calcifies","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"if it sits out there too long .","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"In 2009 and 2010 , congressional Democrats burned nearly 10 months","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"approving ObamaCare .","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"As the King sings ,","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"\" It ' s now or never \" -","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"if Republicans are to repeal and replace ObamaCare .","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"\" Tomorrow will be too late . \"","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"Capitol Attitude is a weekly column","depth":3},{"id":136,"text":"written by members of the Capitol Hill team .","depth":3},{"id":137,"text":"Their articles take you inside the halls of Congress ,","depth":3},{"id":138,"text":"and cover the spectrum of policy issues","depth":4},{"id":139,"text":"being introduced ,","depth":5},{"id":140,"text":"debated","depth":6},{"id":141,"text":"and voted on there .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":283,"left":276,"right":282,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":276,"left":168,"right":275,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":168,"left":145,"right":167,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":145,"left":143,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":167,"left":153,"right":166,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":153,"left":150,"right":152,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":146,"right":149,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":146,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":6,"right":148,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":148,"left":7,"right":147,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":147,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":10,"right":151,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":166,"left":155,"right":165,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":155,"left":13,"right":154,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":154,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":165,"left":16,"right":164,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":164,"left":17,"right":163,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":163,"left":156,"right":162,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":156,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"attribution